HEADWORD: strongbox
<hw>strong"box`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>A box of rigid and
durable construction fitted with a lock, used for the purpose of
protecting valuable items, such as jewelry or money.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> lockbox.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

